---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>El Rinc√≥n del Sabor Fino</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>El Rinc√≥n del Sabor Fino</h1>
      <p>Bienvenidos a una experiencia gastron√≥mica √∫nica</p>
      <div class="nav-buttons">
        <button class="nav-button" onclick="mostrarSeccion('menu')">Ver Men√∫</button>
        <button class="nav-button" onclick="mostrarSeccion('atencion')">Horarios</button>
        <button class="nav-button" onclick="mostrarSeccion('pedido')">Ordenar</button>
